Welcome to the M42 Digital Transformation Collaboration (DTC) Intake Form

Thank you for your interest in partnering with M42 as we work to redefine the future of healthcare through innovation and technology.

This form serves as your official entry point to propose forward-thinking, high-impact collaborations with M42.

It is intended for partners who share our vision for shaping the future of integrated, intelligent healthcare. Whether you are a startup, a global technology provider, or an innovation-driven enterprise, we invite you to complete this form to help us better understand your solution and assess its alignment with M42’s strategic priorities.

We invite proposals that demonstrate measurable value in areas such as AI, digital health, precision medicine, life sciences innovation, and health system optimization. The goal is to advance patient outcomes, improve clinical and operational performance, and co-develop the next generation of health systems.

Please fill out the form with as much relevant detail as possible.

Disclaimer: By submitting any proposal, information, data, idea, concept or other material (collectively, the "Submission") through this portal, you irrevocably acknowledge and agree that the Submission is furnished solely for M42's exploratory and evaluative purposes, and that neither M42 nor any of its affiliates assumes, and each expressly disclaims, any obligation to acknowledge receipt of, review, assess, respond to, engage in further discussions regarding, enter into negotiations concerning, or contractually pursue the Submission in whole or in part. No agency, partnership, joint venture, supplier, fiduciary or other relationship is created or implied between you and M42 as a result of the Submission, and no present or future commitment, undertaking or obligation of any nature whatsoever shall arise on the part of M42 unless and until a duly authorised signatory of M42 executes a definitive written agreement. Any reliance you place upon the possibility of future collaboration with M42 is entirely at your own risk and expense.


